  "instructions": [
    "Preheat a cast-iron skillet over medium-high heat",
    "Season the chicken breast with salt and pepper",
    "Add sesame oil to the skillet and robata-grill the chicken until cooked through",
    "Remove the chicken from the skillet and set aside",
    "Add soy sauce, sake, and mirin to the skillet and bring to a simmer",
    "Add danmuji to the skillet and cook for 2 minutes",
    "Return the chicken to the skillet and stir to combine with the sauce and danmuji",
    "Garnish with green onions and toasted sesame seeds",
    "Serve hot in the cast-iron skillet"
